# Puppet Cron Module

## Notes:
This module manages cronjobs by placing a file in /etc/cron.d.

## Installation:
Install in your puppet master's modulepath

## Usage:
<pre>
cron::job{
  'mysqlbackup'
    minute  => '*',
    hour    => '*',
    date    => '*',
    month   => '*',
    day     => '*',
    user    => 'root',
    command => 'mysqlbackup my_db';
}
</pre>

